```java
		int count = stmt.executeUpdate("delete from t_user where name='wuwang'");
		System.out.println("修改的记录条数为"+count+"条");
```

##### 查询

```java
			String sql2="select empno as a,ename as b,sal as c from emp";
            ResultSet relset=stmt.executeQuery(sql2);
```

#### 5.获得结果集

**注意**：查询语句才会获得结果集对象。

```java
